verbose_text: In an IA mono-iodoacetate (MIA) model of knee OA in rats, IA Supartz FX decreased pain related behavior as well as the number of pain transmitting cells in the dorsal root ganglion, as determined by marker for calcitonin gene related peptide (CGRP).
